    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克批准 27 亿欧元预算赤字应对计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/slovakia-approves-2-7-billion-plan-to-tackle-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克议会通过了一项价值 27 亿欧元（30 亿美元）的整顿方案，以减少欧盟中最高的预算赤字之一，尽管反对派批评该计划可能会损害经济增长，但斯洛伐克议会还是通过了这项方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/slovakia-approves-2-7-billion-plan-to-tackle-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将查戈斯群岛割让给毛里求斯，保留对迭戈加西亚军事基地的控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mauritius-government-agrees-deal-with-uk-on-chagos-archipelago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国达成协议，将印度洋查戈斯群岛的主权割让给毛里求斯，同时保留对具有重要战略意义的英美军事基地的控制权一百年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mauritius-government-agrees-deal-with-uk-on-chagos-archipelago</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:11:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
